Another app which I was using now only lets you save 5 on free version, ONLY because it is made by a well known and more established cyber security company that's been around for decades on PC. I'm assuming a few other more well known ones will be doing the same but this is just as secure as any of them. Love the thumbprint login feature too for quicker access.
